<lb n="8"/>Ēri kaṇṭu tūmpu
<lb n="9"/>Iṭuvi<supplied reason="undefined">ttā</supplied>r
	</p>
        <p>
		I-<hi rend="grantha">dharmma</hi>m ra
<lb break="no" n="10"/><hi rend="grantha">kṣi</hi>ttar aṭi Eṉ
